{"TopicId":205341,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Petition for Squad to make Human Space Program","CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-23T11:38:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-23T11:38:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh boy, I\u0027ve been in the lounge section of the forums for a long time. Maybe this is possible? Just secretly take KSP base code and flood it with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E and other realism mods lol. What am I even doing there. Idk. I just want a realistic stock KSP lol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-23T23:04:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a very bad wrong idea that should never happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo demonstrate exactly why, I present:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022D76DeF4.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002250.00\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/D76DeF4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-24T00:43:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh boy... I remember that one. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-24T01:00:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224046441\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221635030278\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002232993\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022razark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, razark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a very bad wrong idea that should never happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224046476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221635036216\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh boy... I remember that one. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd now we will all have nightmares for a week!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-24T19:52:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni dont think ksp would have been as fun as it is if it weren\u0027t for the kerbals. kerbals and their questionable design choices are what make the game fun. for years i was looking for a newtonian space flight simulator that could hold my interest for more than a couple days. orbiter was boring for lack of a better word. not to say there isnt enough room out there for a more true to life space sim out there for space historians, but i dont think it would be as fun as kerbal is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-24T21:38:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224046711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221635105173\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni dont think ksp would have been as fun as it is if it weren\u0027t for the kerbals. kerbals and their questionable design choices are what make the game fun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m going to jump in... but first, I am NOT speaking for Squad, Intercept, or PD... is is just MY personal opinion... and I agree.\u003Cbr\u003E\nIn the end KSP is still a game... the best game ever IMO... lol.. but still a game.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd the Kerbals add that fun element into what could otherwise be a somewhat boring subject.\u00A0\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nThey have somehow managed to stumble their way to space, and into our hearts. And I just don\u0027t think the game would have been nearly as successful without them\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-25T03:00:52Z\u0022 title=\u002210/25/2021 03:00  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 25, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-27T02:57:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree about the Kerbals\u0027 silliness and that it would have been less fun of a game if it had all the elements of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E \u0026amp; \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E from the start. I like that those are options (they could be easier to set up...and the 30 degree inclination on the solar system makes it unplayable for me) and maybe in KSP 2 they could have a \u0022hard mode\u0022 where the planets are 10x bigger (real scale) and the parts balanced a bit more realistically. For me, personally, there is:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-KSP stock (easy mode)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-KSP with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E \u0026amp; realism mods, etc. (hard mode)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Actually becoming an aerospace engineer in real life (very hard mode)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI almost feel like I might want to regress into easy mode once in a while once I\u0027m doing very hard mode for a job.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-27T05:25:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m for Kerbals of human proportions, for more realistic vessels.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-27T21:55:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224047679\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221635312334\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m for Kerbals of human proportions, for more realistic vessels.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni think this is my only issue with kerbals. if you have ever made a cockpit or command pod mod, you know how awkward it can be to design a cockpit for short creatures with big heads. still you could have my kerbals when you pry them out of my \u003Cs\u003Ecold dead hands\u003C/s\u003E burning space debris.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-27T21:57:07Z\u0022 title=\u002210/27/2021 09:57  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 27, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Staticalliam7","CreatedById":216180,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-14T05:03:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhonestly scott munley program would be amazing\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-14T05:27:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224046476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221635036216\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/24/2021 at 3:43 AM, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_cont